petite bourgois. If you are a heart surgeon making 150k USD a year but you work for a hospital and you aren&#039;t in charge of hiring of firing anyone you are fully proletarian. Labour aristocracy maybe but still proletarian.<br>It is not a question of income, but a question of ones relationship to the means of production.","filename":"0b1d750a9fa062dc237c971e60e1d25886627e58ae4d2479f83a97b40f7d7f3e","ext":".jpg","w":1280,"h":720,"tn_w":125,"tn_h":70,"tim":1491924819626,"time":1491924819,"md5":"HjkdwMECzbf3WMTLDMjCJQ==","fsize":103339,"resto":120610575,"country":"ES","m_img":1,"country_name":"Spain"}]}